excerpt: Prominent Hindu temple featuring hand-carved statues, a large spire & a vegetarian restaurant.
detail_description: Located in Sector 33, the ISKCON Temple Noida is a prominent Hindu temple known for its hand-carved statues and large spire. The seven-story structure stands at approximately 160 feet tall and features various sections including a temple hall, auditorium, guest house, restaurant, and more. This serene oasis offers visitors the opportunity to connect with their inner selves amidst spiritual teachings, art, and culture.
name: ISKCON Temple Noida
address: A-5, Maharaja Agrasen Marg, Opposite Opposite NTPC office, Block A, Sector 33, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201301, India

excerpt: Established in 1990, this 400-hectare wetland includes trails to view many migratory & native birds.
detail_description: Okhla Bird Sanctuary, also known as the Shahid Chandra Shekhar Azad Bird Sanctuary, is a 400-hectare wetland located about 39 km from Delhi's city center. It is a popular spot for photographers, birdwatchers, and nature enthusiasts due to its diverse bird population.
name: Okhla Bird Sanctuary
address: Noida Plaza, N Block, Pocket K, Okhla, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201301, India

excerpt: This amusement park offering over 20 rides & a waterpark with long slides is a popular destination.
detail_description: Worlds of Wonder, located in Noida, is a popular amusement park and waterpark spanning 10 acres. It features over 20 rides and a variety of water-based attractions, making it one of the best water parks in Delhi NCR. The park is divided into four zones and offers 23 world-class attractions, including the thrilling Turbo Tunnel with a 12-meter vertical drop, Boomerango, a Wave Pool, and a Lazy River that winds through half the park.
name: Worlds of Wonder
address: Gate No. 11, Maharaja Agrasen Marg, opposite to Gardens Galleria Mall, near The great india place mall, Sector 38, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201301, India

excerpt: Grand, 7-story shopping center with 330+ stores, including an indoor snow park & many events.
detail_description: DLF Mall of India, located in Sector 18, Noida, Uttar Pradesh, is a grand shopping center spread over 7 floors. It houses more than 330 stores, including international and Indian fashion brands. The mall also features an indoor snow park and a movie theatre with 7 screens. With various dining options and entertainment venues, it offers a holistic shopping experience for visitors.
name: DLF Mall of India, Noida
address: Sector 18, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201301, India

detail_description: Nestled in the bustling urban landscape of Noida, Stupa 18 Gallery stands as a vibrant hub for art enthusiasts and casual visitors alike. Founded in 2010 by mechanical engineer Mahesh Bansal, this gallery is dedicated to showcasing the talents of emerging Indian artists. With an impressive collection that spans abstract paintings, landscapes, figurative works, and sculptures crafted from various media such as oil and watercolor, it offers something for every art lover.
name: Stupa 18 Gallery
address: C/o CRNK 3rd floor, HA 118, Sector 104, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201301, India

excerpt: Sprawling complex of retail shops & restaurants, with a cinema, plus rides & games for children.
detail_description: The Great India Place, also known as GIP, is a massive retail and entertainment complex in Noida. Spanning over 9.47 lakh square feet, it houses 258 brand stores, including popular names like The Body Shop and Vero Moda. Additionally, the mall features anchor stores, a cinema by Carnival Cinemas, a spa, and a 7D movie theatre for an immersive experience.
name: The Great India Place, Noida
address: The great india place mall, Sector 38, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201301, India

detail_description: Atta Market, located in sector 18 of Noida, is a popular destination for affordable shopping. It houses a variety of shops such as New Look Collection and JMD Fashion Zone, offering a wide range of clothing items including jeans, hoodies, shirts, and t-shirts with unique prints and graphics. The market is known for its regular sales on clothes starting from as low as Rs 150.
name: Atta Market
address: Sector 27, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201301, India

excerpt: Buzzy marketplace with indoor & outdoor stalls selling North Indian street food, clothing & spices.
detail_description: Brahmaputra Market is a bustling marketplace in Noida, Uttar Pradesh, offering a vibrant mix of indoor and outdoor stalls selling North Indian street food, clothing, spices, and more. The market comes alive in the evenings with an array of delectable street eats such as tikkas, momos, biryani, pav bhaji, chaats, shawarmas, rolls and South Indian snacks.
name: Brahmaputra Market
address: 865, Maharishi Dayanand Marg, Sector 29, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201303, India

detail_description: KidZania Delhi NCR is a unique entertainment and educational center designed to provide children aged 2 to 16 with an interactive and immersive experience. This life-sized city offers over 100 role-playing activities, allowing kids to learn through play. The concept aims to teach life skills and decision-making through realistic scenarios, while also offering some activities for adults. With its own currency, landscapes, and transportation system, KidZania creates a safe environment for kids to have fun while learning.
name: KidZania Delhi NCR
address: Gate Street, 11, Maharaja Agrasen Marg, near The great india place mall, Sector 38, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201301, India

detail_description: Noida's Botanical Garden is a serene escape from the city, spanning 163 acres and showcasing a diverse range of regional flora. The government has carefully curated this space to protect endangered plant species, offering visitors the chance to see rare plants like Psilotum Nudum and green roses. It's an ideal location for nature photography sessions and leisurely strolls.
name: Botanical Garden
address: Captain Vijyant Thapar Marg, Sector 38, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201301, India

excerpt: Sci-fi-themed snow park in the DLF Mall of India featuring ice skating & sledding.
detail_description: Snow World is a sci-fi-themed snow park located in the DLF Mall of India, Noida. It offers an unforgettable experience with its maintained temperature of about -10 degrees. Visitors can enjoy various snow-related activities such as ice skating, skiing, snowboarding, tobogganing, and playing with snowballs. The park provides all the necessary gear for these activities.
name: Snow World
address: L05, Dlf Mall Of India, Sector 18, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201301, India

excerpt: Shopping mall featuring Venetian-style architecture, canals & gondola rides & an ample food court.
detail_description: The Grand Venice Mall, also known as TGV mall, is an Italian-themed shopping center that aims to recreate the magic of Venice. With its Venetian-style architecture, canals, and gondola rides, it offers a unique experience for visitors. The mall features replicas of famous Venetian structures like the Leaning Tower of Pisa and Roman sculptures. It's not just a shopping destination but also an architectural delight and entertainment spot.
name: The Grand Venice Mall
address: Plot No SH3, Site IV, near Pari Chowk, Greater Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201308, India

excerpt: Religious site also known as the Bahá’í House of Worship, opened in 1986 to those of all religions.
detail_description: The Lotus Temple, also known as the Bahá’í House of Worship, is a religious site that opened in 1986 and welcomes people of all religions. This distinctive place of worship in South Delhi resembles India's national flower with its ethereal marble construction. The temple's nine overlapping walls enclose a single cavernous interior space, reflecting the Bahai Temples' practice of being open to all.
name: Lotus Temple
address: Lotus Temple Rd Bahapur, Kalkaji, New Delhi, Delhi 110019, India

detail_description: The GIP mall, commonly known as The Great India Place Mall, caters to the younger generation and houses a diverse range of stores and labels that provide products and services in a centralized location. This unique shopping center is renowned for fulfilling all your requirements, boasting numerous nightclubs and cinema theaters within its premises.
name: The great india place mall
address: 327, Sector 38, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201301, India

detail_description: Noida Haat is a newly developed 10-acre space in Noida that showcases traditional Indian handicrafts and handmade products from all over the country. It features a food bazaar and aims to promote art and culture. Visitors can explore various shops offering items like pottery, carpets, Bengali sarees, leather bags, pickles, namkeens, and dry fruits from Kabul and Kashmir.
name: Noida Haat
address: D-10, Prakash Hospital Marg, Block D, Sector 32, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201307, India

detail_description: The Okhla Bird Sanctuary is an unexpected gem nestled near the Noida Delhi border. It features a vast lake bordered by a highway on one side and endless water on the other. Visitors can enjoy tranquil sunsets and connect with nature in this serene setting.
name: Okhla Bird sanctuary
address: H75W+J72, Part 1 Abul Fazal Enclave, Abul Fazal Enclave, Part-1 Block D, Jamia Nagar, Okhla, New Delhi, Delhi 110025, India

detail_description: The Irish House in Noida is a lively pub located on the 4th floor of DLF Mall, offering a vibrant atmosphere for beer enthusiasts, sports fans, and food lovers. With its rustic wooden ambiance, large community tables, and high barstools, it provides an inviting space for socializing. The menu features a variety of non-vegetarian and vegetarian dishes paired with chilled drinks and mocktails.
name: The Irish House, Noida
address: 4th Floor, Dlf Mall Of India, Plot No. M 03, NCR, Sector 18, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201301, India

detail_description: Appu Ghar Express, situated at The Great India Place in Sector 38A, is a popular family entertainment destination. Boasting 16 thrilling bowling lanes, it caters to both beginners and experienced bowlers. Additionally, the venue offers arcade games and pool tables for a well-rounded entertainment experience. As the country's first indoor amusement park, it features separate zones for various age groups and corporate events.
name: Appu Ghar Express
address: Bldg no-105, The great india place mall, Plot No- A-2, nr. TGIP MAll, Sector 38, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201301, India

detail_description: Sacked Newton is a top restaurant in Noida known for its innovative dining concept and delicious fusion cuisine. The building itself is impressive, and the restaurant offers a fantastic sushi bar with options for both vegetarians and non-vegetarians. In addition to their mouthwatering sushi, they also serve Mediterranean, Italian, North Indian, and Continental dishes. The menu is inspired by Isaac Newton and features a mix of global flavors presented in a playful way.
name: I Sacked Newton
address: 5th floor, Logix mall, Wave City Center, Sector 32, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201301, India

detail_description: Smaaash is a popular entertainment center in Noida that offers a unique and high-end gaming experience for both young and adult visitors. The venue features a variety of activities including bowling, cricket, laser tag, virtual reality gaming, and more. With its innovative technology, Smaaash provides an adventurous atmosphere for guests to enjoy. The facility also includes a food court for convenient dining options.
name: Smaaash
address: GF –16 & GF - 17, Plot No.C3, E1, Sector 129, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201304, India
